  "page": "Lord of Hellgate Hall",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of Hellgate Hall</b> was one of the hereditary titles of the lords of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dryland\" title=\"House Dryland\">House Dryland</a>, who styled themselves as <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Brimstone\" title=\"King of the Brimstone\">Kings</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brimstone\" title=\"Brimstone\">Brimstone</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> prior to <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria%27s_War\" title=\"Nymeria&#39;s War\">Nymeria's War</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Lords_of_Hellgate_Hall\">Known Lords of Hellgate Hall</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Hellgate_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Lords of Hellgate Hall\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Lucifer_Dryland\" title=\"Lucifer Dryland\">Lucifer Dryland</a>, King of the Brimstone and Lord of Hellgate Hall</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Hellgate_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.